   <h1>üö¢ New Freight Request</h1>\n      <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px;\">OMEGO Marketplace</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"content\">\n      <div class=\"request-id\">${requestData.request_id}</div>\n      \n      <p>Dear ${forwarderData.company_name},</p>\n      \n      <p>A new freight request has been posted on the OMEGO platform that matches your expertise. Please review the details below and submit your competitive quotation.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"details\">\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üìç Origin:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.origin}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üìç Destination:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.destination}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üì¶ Cargo Type:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.cargo_type}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">‚öñÔ∏è Weight:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.weight_kg} kg</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üìê Dimensions:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.dimensions || 'Not specified'}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üìã Incoterms:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.incoterms}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail-row\">\n          <span class=\"label\">üìù Special Requirements:</span>\n          <span class=\"value\">${requestData.special_requirements || 'None'}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"highlight-box\">\n        <strong>‚è∞ IMPORTANT: First 3 Quotes Win!</strong><br>\n        This request will automatically close once <strong>3 quotations</strong> are received. Submit your quote quickly to secure your spot!\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"instructions\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #2E75B6;\">üìß How to Submit Your Quotation:</h3>\n        <p><strong>Simply REPLY to this email</strong> with your quote including:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Total price</strong> (with currency, e.g., USD 2,500)</li>\n          <li><strong>Transit time</strong> (in days)</li>\n          <li><strong>Validity period</strong> (e.g., 7 days)</li>\n          <li><strong>Carrier/shipping line</strong> (e.g., Maersk, CMA CGM)</li>\n          <li><strong>Service type</strong> (e.g., FCL Direct, LCL)</li>\n          <li><strong>Any additional charges or terms</strong></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è CRITICAL:</strong> Keep the Request ID (<strong>${requestData.request_id}</strong>) in your reply subject line. Our AI system uses this to match your quote.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n        <a href=\"mailto:quote@omegoonline.com?subject=RE: ${requestData.request_id} Quote\" class=\"cta-button\">\n          üìß Reply with Your Quote\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      \n      <p style=\"margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;\">\n        <strong>Note:</strong> Only registered and approved forwarders can submit quotations. Your quote will be processed by our AI system and presented to the customer along with other competitive quotes.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <p><strong>OMEGO Freight Forwarding Platform</strong></p>\n      <p>This is an automated notification. Replies will be processed by our AI system.</p>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">¬© 2024 OMEGO. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n`;\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    email_to: forwarderData.email,\n    email_subject: emailSubject,\n    email_body: emailBody,\n    forwarder_id: forwarderData.forwarder_id,\n    forwarder_company: forwarderData.company_name,\n    request_id: requestData.request_id\n  }\n};"
